  "prompt": "Which are the 4 stroke bikes in India?",
  "response": "Okay, almost all modern motorcycles sold in India are 4-stroke.  2-stroke engines are largely obsolete due to emissions regulations. To narrow it down and give you a more useful list, I'll categorize popular 4-stroke bikes available in India by type:\n\n**Commuter Bikes (Fuel Efficient and Practical):**\n\n*   **Hero Splendor Plus:** A classic and one of the best-selling motorcycles in India. Known for its reliability and fuel efficiency.\n*   **Hero HF Deluxe:** Another very popular and affordable commuter bike from Hero.\n*   **Bajaj CT110X/CT125X:** Rugged and durable commuter bikes designed for tough conditions.\n*   **TVS Sport:** A budget-friendly option with decent fuel efficiency.\n*   **Honda Shine 100/125:** Refined and reliable commuter bikes from Honda.\n*   **Hero Passion Pro:** A stylish commuter bike with a comfortable ride.\n\n**Scooters (Automatic Transmission):**\n\n*   **Honda Activa 6G:** The best-selling scooter in India, known for its reliability and ease of use.\n*   **TVS Jupiter:** A very popular scooter with a focus on comfort and features.\n*   **Suzuki Access 125:** A powerful and refined scooter with a good balance of performance and fuel efficiency.\n*   **Hero MotoCorp Destini 125:** A comfortable and stylish scooter.\n*   **Ola S1 Pro:** An electric scooter with long range and advanced features.\n*   **Ather 450X:** A premium electric scooter known for its performance and technology.\n\n**Sports/Naked Bikes (Performance-Oriented):**\n\n*   **Yamaha R15 V4:** A popular entry-level sports bike with a sporty design and good handling.\n*   **Yamaha MT-15:** A naked streetfighter version of the R15, with aggressive styling.\n*   **Bajaj Pulsar NS200/RS200:** Popular and affordable performance bikes.\n*   **TVS Apache RTR 160 4V/ RTR 200 4V:** Sporty and feature-rich bikes with good performance.\n*   **KTM Duke 125/200/250/390:** Aggressive and powerful naked bikes.\n*   **Royal Enfield Continental GT 650:** A cafe racer style bike with a powerful parallel-twin engine.\n*   **Royal Enfield Interceptor 650:** A classic roadster with a comfortable riding position.\n*   **BMW G310R:** A premium naked bike with German engineering.\n\n**Cruiser Bikes:**\n\n*   **Royal Enfield Classic 350:** An iconic cruiser with a retro design and comfortable riding position.\n*   **Royal Enfield Meteor 350:** A modern cruiser with a smooth engine and comfortable ergonomics.\n*   **Bajaj Avenger Cruise 220:** An affordable cruiser with a laid-back riding experience.\n*   **Jawa Standard/42:** Retro-styled cruisers with a distinctive look.\n*   **Yezdi Roadster/Scrambler/Adventure:** Modern cruisers with a focus on performance and features.\n*   **Benelli Imperiale 400:** A classic cruiser with a comfortable riding position.\n\n**Adventure Bikes:**\n\n*   **Royal Enfield Himalayan:** An affordable adventure bike designed for off-road riding.\n*   **Hero XPulse 200 4V:** A lightweight and versatile adventure bike.\n*   **BMW G310 GS:** A premium adventure bike with German engineering.\n*   **KTM Adventure 250/390:** Powerful and capable adventure bikes.\n*   **Suzuki V-Strom SX:** An adventure tourer with a comfortable riding position and good performance.\n\n**Important Considerations:**\n\n*   **Displacement:**  The engine size (cc) affects power and performance.\n*   **Budget:** Prices vary widely, so set a budget before you start looking.\n*   **Riding Style:** Consider how you'll use the bike (commuting, touring, off-roading) to choose the right type.\n*   **Features:** Look for features like ABS (Anti-lock Braking System), digital instrument clusters, and fuel injection.\n\n**Where to Find More Information:**\n\n*   **Manufacturer Websites:**  Hero MotoCorp, Honda, Bajaj Auto, TVS Motor Company, Royal Enfield, Yamaha, KTM, Suzuki, BMW Motorrad, Jawa, Yezdi\n*   **Online Automotive Portals:**  ZigWheels, CarAndBike, Autocar India, BikeDekho\n\nBefore making a purchase, I highly recommend visiting a dealership, taking a test ride, and comparing different models to find the perfect fit for your needs and preferences.\n",
